msgstr "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:9
msgid ""
"`ptool.fs.read(path)` reads a file as raw bytes and returns a Lua string."
msgstr ""
"`ptool.fs.read(path)` lê um arquivo como bytes brutos e retorna uma string "
"Lua."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:11
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:11"
msgid "`path` (string, required): The file path."
msgstr "`path` (string, obrigatório): O caminho do arquivo."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:12
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:12"
msgid "Returns: `string`."
msgstr "Retorna: `string`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:14
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:14"
msgid "Notes:"
msgstr "Notas:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:16
msgid ""
"The returned Lua string contains the file bytes exactly as stored on disk."
msgstr "A string Lua retornada contém exatamente os bytes armazenados em disco."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:17
msgid ""
"Text files continue to work as before, but binary files are also supported."
msgstr ""
"Arquivos de texto continuam funcionando como antes, e agora arquivos "
"binários também são suportados."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:19
