msgstr "`Unreleased` - Introduced."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:55
msgid ""
"`ptool.fs.append(path, content)` appends a Lua string to a file as raw "
"bytes. If the file does not exist, it is created."
msgstr ""
"`ptool.fs.append(path, content)` acrescenta uma string Lua ao final de um "
"arquivo como bytes brutos. Se o arquivo não existir, ele será criado."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:58
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:58"
msgid "`path` (string, required): The file path."
msgstr "`path` (string, obrigatório): O caminho do arquivo."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:59
msgid "`content` (string, required): The content to append."
msgstr "`content` (string, obrigatório): O conteúdo a acrescentar."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:61
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:61"
msgid "Notes:"
msgstr "Notas:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:63
msgid "`content` is written byte-for-byte at the end of the file."
msgstr "`content` é gravado byte por byte no final do arquivo."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:64
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:64"
msgid "Embedded NUL bytes and non-UTF-8 bytes are preserved."
msgstr "Bytes NUL embutidos e bytes não UTF-8 são preservados."

