#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:113
msgid ""
"`File` represents an open local file handle returned by `ptool.fs.open()`."
msgstr ""
"`File` representa um identificador de arquivo local aberto retornado por "
"`ptool.fs.open()`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:115
msgid "It is implemented as a Lua userdata."
msgstr "Ele é implementado como um userdata do Lua."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:117
msgid "Methods:"
msgstr "Métodos:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:119
msgid "`file:read([n])` -> `string`"
msgstr "`file:read([n])` -> `string`"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:120
msgid "`file:write(content)` -> `nil`"
msgstr "`file:write(content)` -> `nil`"

